INSTALLATION NOTES

Create a "Custom Block" to be positioned in region "Sidebar1".

Paste the contents of FilteredGroups.txt into the block content.

The block should be configured as follows:

Title: FILTER GROUPS:
Description:   Filter Collaboration Groups View
Text Format:  PHP Code  ** You will need to enable the PHP input filter module

On "Visibility Settings->Pages" check "Only the listed pages"
Enter the following value for pages:  collaboration*